// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2025-0661 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 8ee39e69-cd3b-5b29-a28f-dd1526772ecf

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:22.04*")
